&lt;p&gt;哪怕在胖猫跳江后几天，
谭某还是继续到处撩骚钓鱼，&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://www.wangluojishi.com/images/%E8%83%96%E7%8C%AB/%E8%83%96%E7%8C%AB%E8%B0%AD%E7%AB%B9%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6%E6%9C%80%E5%85%A8%E8%A7%A3%E6%9E%90%E5%AD%98%E6%A1%A3%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95/de5bfbce-2aaf-4346-877e-c4ad7ab56aec.png&#34; alt=&#34;image&#34;&gt;
